---
---
<section style="min-height:92vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding-top:2rem;">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p style="font-size:.8rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent-light);margin-bottom:1.25rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;">
      <span style="display:inline-block;width:2rem;height:1px;background:var(--accent-light);"></span>
      Halo, saya
    </p>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(2.75rem,7vw,5rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.05;margin-bottom:1.25rem;letter-spacing:-.02em;">
      <span style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff 30%,#a78bfa);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;">
        Azijul Akbar
      </span>
      <br />
      <span style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#a78bfa,#60a5fa);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;">
        Nur Fatihah
      </span>
    </h1>
    <p style="font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--muted);max-width:480px;margin-bottom:2.5rem;line-height:1.7;">
      3D Artist yang membangun aset game dari konsep hingga siap digunakan, fokus pada modeling low poly dan performa di dalam game.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="#projects" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));color:#fff;padding:.7rem 1.75rem;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;transition:opacity .2s;box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(124,58,237,.3);" onmouseover="this.style.opacity='.85'" onmouseout="this.style.opacity='1'">
        Lihat Proyek
      </a>
      <a href="#contact" style="border:1px solid var(--border);padding:.7rem 1.75rem;border-radius:8px;color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;transition:all .2s;backdrop-filter:blur(8px);" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='rgba(167,139,250,.4)';this.style.color='var(--text)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='var(--border)';this.style.color='var(--muted)'">
        Hubungi Saya
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Floating orbs -->
  <div style="position:absolute;right:10%;top:30%;width:320px;height:320px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(124,58,237,.15),transparent 70%);filter:blur(40px);pointer-events:none;animation:float 6s ease-in-out infinite;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;right:20%;top:50%;width:200px;height:200px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(37,99,235,.12),transparent 70%);filter:blur(30px);pointer-events:none;animation:float 8s ease-in-out infinite reverse;"></div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
  }
</style>
